Package: StackbarExtended
Title: Stacked Bar Graph And Differential Abundance Analysis For Microbiota Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thibault", "Cuisiniere", ,"thibault.cuisiniere@umontreal.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7325-9476"))
Description: StackbarExtended provide tool for visualizing and analyzing gut microbiota compositions through clustered stacked bar plots. Designed to work with phyloseq-class objects, it enables users to cluster taxa by phylogeny and highlight differentially abundant features. It accepts a wide range of parameters for detailed customization, including experimental group selection, taxa abundance thresholds, and color schemes, allowing publication-ready graphs creation. 
License: GPL-3
